cs.NE, cs.CL, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.CV. 

The paper proposes a novel recurrent neural network architecture and evaluates it on language modeling and program evaluation tasks. This suggests that the paper could belong to several sub-categories, including cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing) for the proposed architecture, cs.CL (Computation and Language) for the language modeling task, cs.LG (Machine Learning) for the evaluation of different RNN units, cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) for the overall approach, and cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition) for the program evaluation task.
